            "category": "crypto",
            "date": "2025-04-02",
            "headline": "ETH price may have bottomed, but pro traders show little interest; at $1,768 low, it's struggled to reach $2,000. Year-to-date, Ether is 44% down with futures metrics indicating lack of bullish sentiment. Ether's dominance in DeFi remains strong despite DApps revenue drop. Whale hesitance seen in ETH options market, while retail trading enthusiasm wanes due to ETH ETFs. Overall cautious outlook on ETH price.",
