            "headline": "Specialty retailers Wayfair, Williams-Sonoma see shares drop after RH misses Q4 estimates with revenue at $812.41 million and EPS at $1.58 vs expected revenue of $829.56 million and EPS of $1.92, citing softening demand due to spiked mortgage rates.",
